{"word":"λιλαίομαι","slug":"λιλαίομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n63270\" key=\"lilai/omai\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">λῐλαίομαι</orth>, only <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ pres.\">pres.</a></tns> and <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ impf.\">impf.</a></tns>, <sense id=\"n63270.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">long</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">desire earnestly</tr_>, freq. in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author></bibl>, mostly c. <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ inf.\">inf.</a></mood>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">long to be</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">do</tr_> so and so, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τίμε . . λιλαίεαι ἠπεροπεύειν</foreign>; <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:399\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.399</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">λ. πολεμίζειν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:16:89\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.89</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εὐνηθῆναι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:14:331\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.331</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: metaph., of a lance, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">λιλαιομένη χροὸς ἆσαι</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">longing</tr_> to taste flesh, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:168\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.168</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:574\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.574</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:15:317\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.317</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">λιλαιομένη πόσιν εἶναι</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">longing for him</tr_> to be her husband, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1:15\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.15</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:9:30\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.30</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:32\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">32</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:23:334\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.334</biblScope> </bibl>: c. gen., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">long for</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πολέμοιο, ὁδοῖο, βιότοιο, δόρποιο</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:133\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.133</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1:315\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.315</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:12:328\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.328</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.t